'''Marsh lizards''' were a [[Species/Legends|species]] of large scaly [[Snake/Legends|serpents]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Trinta]]. The creatures grew up to two meters long, had sharp teeth, and a spiked tail. Marsh lizards preferred to bask in the sun on islands and mudbanks.

